ml_tags: In Loving Memory Of Our  Beloved Father Sunrise:May 01, 1964 Sunset: June 09, 2020 Alifeleti Paea I' Ma'ananga Mo'onia Ko hoku tauhi a Sihova; e ikai teu masiva. Oku ne fakatokoto au i he ngaahi ngoue lau mauiui; Oku ne tataki au i he ngaahi tafetafemalie. Oku ne fakamoui hoku Laumalie, hala oe maonioni koeuhi ko hono huafa. Io, Ne ongo eku eveeva i he telea oe akau mo ho tokotoko oku na fakafiemalie au. Oku ke teuteu ae keinangaanga maaku i he ao hoku ngaahi fili: oku ke pani aki hoku ulu ae lolo: oku fonu mahuohua a eku ipu. Koe mooni e muimui iate au ae lelei moe aloofa i he aho malumalu oe mate, E ikai teu manavahe ki ha kovi; he oku ke iate au; Ko hoo vaa Oku ne tataki au ki he vee vai oku kotoape o eku moui; pea teu nofo i he fale o Sihova o Lauikuoga.
